{
  "id": "cli/new",
  "title": "ng new",
  "contents": "\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/commands/new.json?message=docs(...)%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/v11.2.0-rc.0/packages/angular/cli/commands/new.json\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/new\", \"name\": \"new\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-new\">ng new<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/new#ng-new\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">创建一个新工作空间和一个初始 Angular 应用。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Creates a new workspace and an initial Angular application.</p>\n\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading no-auto-link\">ng <span class=\"cli-name\">new</span> &#x3C;<var>name</var>> [<var>options</var>]</code-example>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading no-auto-link\">ng <span class=\"cli-name\">n</span> &#x3C;<var>name</var>> [<var>options</var>]</code-example>\n\n\n\n    \n    <h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"mode_edit---code----------说明\">\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/commands/new.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/v11.2.0-rc.0/packages/angular/cli/commands/new.md\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n        说明\n    </h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">创建并初始化一个新的 Angular 应用程序，该应用程序是新工作区的默认项目。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Creates and initializes a new Angular application that is the default project for a new workspace.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">提供交互式提示以提供可选配置，例如添加路由支持。可以放心地为所有提示选择其默认值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Provides interactive prompts for optional configuration, such as adding routing support.\nAll prompts can safely be allowed to default.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">新的工作空间文件夹名称就是指定的项目名称，并且在顶层包含了配置文件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The new workspace folder is given the specified project name, and contains configuration files at the top level.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">默认情况下，新的初始应用程序（与工作空间名称相同）的文件放置在 <code>src/</code> 子文件夹中。相应的端到端测试位于 <code>e2e/</code> 子文件夹中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">By default, the files for a new initial application (with the same name as the workspace) are placed in the <code>src/</code> subfolder. Corresponding end-to-end tests are placed in the <code>e2e/</code> subfolder.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">新应用程序的配置位于工作区配置文件 <code>angular.json</code> 中 <code>projects</code> 部分的项目名称下。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The new application's configuration appears in the <code>projects</code> section of the <code>angular.json</code> workspace configuration file, under its project name.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">你在工作空间中生成的后续应用程序位于 <code>projects/</code> 子文件夹中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Subsequent applications that you generate in the workspace reside in the <code>projects/</code> subfolder.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你计划在工作空间中放多个应用程序，则可以通过将 <code>--createApplication</code> 选项设置为 false 来创建一个空的工作空间。然后，你可以使用 <code>ng generate application</code> 创建一个初始应用程序。这能让工作空间的名称不同于初始应用程序的名称，并确保所有应用程序都位于 <code>/projects</code> 子文件夹中，并与配置文件的结构匹配。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If you plan to have multiple applications in the workspace, you can create an empty workspace by setting the <code>--createApplication</code> option to false.\nYou can then use <code>ng generate application</code> to create an initial application.\nThis allows a workspace name different from the initial app name, and ensures that all applications reside in the <code>/projects</code> subfolder, matching the structure of the configuration file.</p>\n\n\n    \n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"arguments\">参数</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>参数</th>\n      <th>说明</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">&#x3C;<var>name</var>></code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p>The name of the new workspace and initial project.</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">选项</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>选项</th>\n      <th>说明</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--collection=<var>collection</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">用来生成初始应用的一组原理图。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A collection of schematics to use in generating the initial application.</p>\n\n\n        \n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名：</span> -c</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--commit=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Initial git repository commit information.</p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--create-application=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Create a new initial application project in the 'src' folder of the new workspace. When false, creates an empty workspace with no initial application. You can then use the generate application command so that all applications are created in the projects folder.</p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">true</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--defaults=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">对有默认值的选项禁用交互式输入提示。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Disable interactive input prompts for options with a default.</p>\n\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--directory=<var>directory</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>The directory name to create the workspace in.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--dry-run=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">运行一遍并汇报其活动轨迹，但不真的写入任何结果。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Run through and reports activity without writing out results.</p>\n\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名：</span> -d</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--force=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">强制覆盖现存文件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Force overwriting of existing files.</p>\n\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名：</span> -f</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--help=<br>    true|false|json|JSON</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">在控制台显示关于本命令的帮助信息。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Shows a help message for this command in the console.</p>\n\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--inline-style=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Include styles inline in the component TS file. By default, an external styles file is created and referenced in the component TypeScript file.</p>\n\n        \n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名：</span> -s</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--inline-template=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Include template inline in the component TS file. By default, an external template file is created and referenced in the component TypeScript file.</p>\n\n        \n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名：</span> -t</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--interactive=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">启用交互式输入提示。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Enable interactive input prompts.</p>\n\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--legacy-browsers=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Add support for legacy browsers like Internet Explorer using differential loading.</p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--minimal=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Create a workspace without any testing frameworks. (Use for learning purposes only.)</p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--new-project-root=<br>    <var>new-project-root</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>The path where new projects will be created, relative to the new workspace root.</p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">projects</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--package-manager=<br>    npm|yarn|pnpm|cnpm</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>The package manager used to install dependencies.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--prefix=<var>prefix</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>The prefix to apply to generated selectors for the initial project.</p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">app</code></p>\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名：</span> -p</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--routing=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Generate a routing module for the initial project.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--skip-git=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Do not initialize a git repository.</p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名：</span> -g</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--skip-install=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Do not install dependency packages.</p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--skip-tests=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Do not generate \"spec.ts\" test files for the new project.</p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名：</span> -S</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--strict=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Creates a workspace with stricter type checking and stricter bundle budgets settings. This setting helps improve maintainability and catch bugs ahead of time. For more information, see <a href=\"https://angular.io/guide/strict-mode\">https://angular.io/guide/strict-mode</a></p>\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--style=<br>    css|scss|sass|less|styl</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>The file extension or preprocessor to use for style files.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--verbose=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p translation-result=\"on\">在输出日志中添加更多详情。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Add more details to output logging.</p>\n\n\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-default\">默认值：</span> <code class=\"no-auto-link\">false</code></p>\n        <p no-translate=\"\"><span class=\"cli-aliases\">别名：</span> -v</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--view-encapsulation=<br>    Emulated|Native|None|ShadowDom</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>The view encapsulation strategy to use in the initial project.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/router-tutorial-toh\n - guide/visual-studio-2015\n - start/start-deployment\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - cli/new#ng-new\n - https://angular.io/guide/strict-mode\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/commands/new.json?message=docs(...)%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/angular/cli/commands/new.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/v11.2.0-rc.0/packages/angular/cli/commands/new.json\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/v11.2.0-rc.0/packages/angular/cli/commands/new.md\n-->"
}